data.description:
The Boat House is a family-owned multi-store boat dealer & marine services provider that has been serving its local boating communities across the Midwest and Florida for over 30 years. The Boat House Group includes 8 Midwest locations and 3 Florida locations offering: New & Used Boat Sales, On Site and Mobile Service, Storage, Parts, Pro Shop, Pier and Lift Services, Boat Clubs, In-House Financing, Consignments, On Water Demonstrations, Boating Education Courses, Community Boating Events, and more.

MIDWEST LOCATIONS
- The Boat House Chicago - Johnsburg, IL
- The Boat House Lake Geneva - Lake Geneva, WI
- The Boat House Lauderdale Lakes - Elkhorn, WI
- The Boat House Whitewater - Whitewater, WI
- The Boat House Lake Country - Nashotah & Milwaukee, WI
- The Boat House Door County - Sister Bay, WI
- The Boat House Three Lakes - Three Lakes, WI

FLORIDA LOCATIONS
- The Boat House Cape Coral - Cape Coral, FL
- The Boat House Naples - Naples, FL
- The Boat House Port Charlotte - Port Charlotte, FL

"Our core purpose is sharing knowledge that builds confidence and passion for the boating lifestyle to create lifelong memories with family and friends."
